title: The Official Programme  2012 Olympic Games - 27 Jul 12 Aug 2012
description: The Official Programme of the London 2012 Olympic Games is a souvenir to be cherished. This beautifully designed 196-page publication is a complete guide to the Games: the athletes (from Team GB and other nations), venues, people behind the scenes, history, the London 2012 Festival, facts and figures and legacy. The Official Programme also includes the competition schedule and a comprehensive A-Z of all 26 Olympic sports.
